"""
Free algebra elements

AUTHOR: David Kohel, 2005-09

TESTS:
    sage: R.<x,y> = FreeAlgebra(QQ,2)
    sage: x == loads(dumps(x))
    True
    sage: x*y
    x*y
    sage: (x*y)^0
    1
    sage: (x*y)^3
    x*y*x*y*x*y
"""

